  "message": "viz: perf + UI polish, OG share images, meta tags\n\n8-phase optimization of spec evolution visualization:\n- Data caching (parse once, filter on re-render)\n- Input debouncing + impact slider bug fix\n- Singleton caches (markdownit, bucketById map)\n- Bucket toggles DOM caching\n- Commit list DOM caching + progressive rendering\n- highlight.js re-highlight guard\n- CSS containment + will-change hints\n- UI layout refinements (dock, mobile, KPIs)\n\nAdd OpenGraph/Twitter Card meta tags and share images\n(1200x630 og-image.png, 1200x600 twitter-image.png).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
